remarks: Elimination rule identical to ~ mp2an .  The non-virtual deduction form is the virtual deduction form, which is ~ mp2an .  (Contributed by Alan Sare, 15-Jun-2011.)  (Proof modification is discouraged.) (New usage is discouraged.)
statement:
e00an.1 $e |- ph $.
e00an.2 $e |- ps $.
e00an.3 $e |- ( ( ph /\ ps ) -> ch ) $.
e00an $p |- ch $.
